統強權，七度奪得非洲盃冠軍。由薩拉赫領軍的法老軍團，擁有非洲最出色的攻擊火力。</p></div></div><section class=\"mb-8\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">小組積分（即時）</h2><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"px-4 py-3\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4b1cc3,#3a15a0)\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold\">G<!-- --> 組積分表</h3></div><div class=\"p-6 text-center text-gray-400 text-sm\">載入中…</div></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">球員名單</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"bg-gray-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700\">守門員</div><div class=\"divide-y divide-gray-50\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2.5 hover:bg-blue-50/50 transition-colors\" href=\"/players/egypt-mohamed-el-shenawy\"><span class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono font-bold text-gray-500\">1</span><div class=\"flex-1\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-800\">埃爾舍納維</span><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 ml-2\">Mohamed El Shenawy</span></div><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">37<!-- -->歲</span><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">Al Ahly</span></a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2.5 hover:bg-blue-50/50 transition-colors\" href=\"/players/egypt-mahdy-soliman\"><span class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono font-bold text-gray-500\">16</span><div class=\"flex-1\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-800\">Mahdy Soliman</span><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 ml-2\">Mahdy Soliman</span></div><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">39<!-- -->歲</span><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">Zamalek</span></a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2.5 hover:bg-blue-50/50 transition-colors\" href=\"/players/egypt-mostafa-shoubir\"><span class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-gray-100 flex items-ce